{
  "logNo": "220745532227",
  "title": "우리 회식했어요~  -남성역 경희 이수한의원-",
  "addDate": "2016. 6. 25.",
  "categoryNo": "43",
  "parentCategoryNo": "1",
  "url": "https://blog.naver.com/PostView.naver?blogId=isuhani&logNo=220745532227",
  "html_size": 204903,
  "body": "<div id=\"post-view220745532227\" class=\"post-view pcol2 _param(1) _postViewArea220745532227\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div style=\"font-size:10pt; font-family:'957317_10';\" class=\"view\"><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이수한의원 식구들~&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오래간만에 회식을 했습니다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘의 메뉴는&nbsp;'일식'</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">상호는 \"가네미\"</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;식당이 아기자기하니</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">조명도 은은하고</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">분위기도 좋았다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">손님은 어찌나 많은지</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">주문이 많아서 우리 음식이 좀 늦게 나오긴 했지만</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그래도 맛있으니깐 봐준다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅎㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_212/isuhani_1466816203535jcMna_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161440100.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_212/isuhani_1466816203535jcMna_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161440100.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_212/isuhani_1466816203535jcMna_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161440100.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_289/isuhani_1466816204067nrakG_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161440525.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 853px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_289/isuhani_1466816204067nrakG_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161440525.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_289/isuhani_1466816204067nrakG_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161440525.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이건.. 사케? </p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">적응할수 없는 맛</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅋㅋ<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_282/isuhani_1466816204439HokUL_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441160.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 853px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_282/isuhani_1466816204439HokUL_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441160.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_282/isuhani_1466816204439HokUL_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441160.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">따뜻한 우동도 나오고..</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">자.. 첫 메뉴가 나옵니다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\"산해진미\"</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">해삼내장을 곁들인 모듬해물</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이라고 설명하면 되려나?<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_1466816204813IYB8l_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441502.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"600\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 600px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_4/isuhani_1466816204813IYB8l_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441502.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_1466816204813IYB8l_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441502.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오징어 연어 게살 낙지 새우 등 위에 해삼이 있는건데..</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">처음에는 해삼때문에 비려서 못먹을줄 알았는데</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">나름 괜찮았다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛있음 ㅋㅋㅋ <br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_286/isuhani_1466816205255SmEEH_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441831.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"551\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 551px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_286/isuhani_1466816205255SmEEH_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441831.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_286/isuhani_1466816205255SmEEH_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161441831.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그래도 해삼냄새랑 맛때문에 조금 힘들어서</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">간장에 푹 찍어먹었지만 </p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">굿!</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">다음 메뉴는 '와규타다끼'</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">타다끼라 했으나 와규숙주볶음이 맞을 듯<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_252/isuhani_1466816205672SF6kJ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442144.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"564\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 564px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_252/isuhani_1466816205672SF6kJ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442144.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_252/isuhani_1466816205672SF6kJ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442144.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">요것도 참 맛있었다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">세번째 메뉴는 누가봐도 모듬회 <br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_55/isuhani_1466816205991eXhdJ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442697.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"506\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 506px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_55/isuhani_1466816205991eXhdJ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442697.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_55/isuhani_1466816205991eXhdJ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442697.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛있게 먹으면서 한컷<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_14668162063403TtDi_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442966.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_4/isuhani_14668162063403TtDi_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442966.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_14668162063403TtDi_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161442966.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">일식집가면 빠질수 없죠</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">초밥~<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_1466816206686r17Pj_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443231.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 853px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_4/isuhani_1466816206686r17Pj_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443231.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_1466816206686r17Pj_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443231.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">초밥도 맛있었는데</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이미 3가지 음식이나 먹어서</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;이수한의원 식구들 모두</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">배가 슬슬 불러와서</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">많이 못먹었다능 ㅠ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그래도 먹을수 있는만큼은&nbsp;많이&nbsp;먹어서 다행이다 ㅋ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;난 항상 회식때 너무 먹는다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">(모두가 아니깐 안비밀ㅎㅎㅎㅎ)</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_262/isuhani_1466816207087X7Rms_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443492.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_262/isuhani_1466816207087X7Rms_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443492.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_262/isuhani_1466816207087X7Rms_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443492.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_64/isuhani_14668162073900QcmD_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443861.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"542\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 542px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_64/isuhani_14668162073900QcmD_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443861.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_64/isuhani_14668162073900QcmD_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161443861.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">계란 초밥은 달아서 맛있다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">나는 아기입맛인듯 </p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅎㅎ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그리고 2차로 근처에있는</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">독일 수제 소세지를 파는..\"Urban Knife\"라는 곳을 갔다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_18/isuhani_1466816207695O3L5b_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501694.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_18/isuhani_1466816207695O3L5b_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501694.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_18/isuhani_1466816207695O3L5b_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501694.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">들어갔는데</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">소세지들이 주렁주렁</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_85/isuhani_1466816207991RPbNA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161502028.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_85/isuhani_1466816207991RPbNA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161502028.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_85/isuhani_1466816207991RPbNA_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161502028.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">그 밑에 냉장고에도 소세지가 가득~<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_1466816208302oWyQc_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501377.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_4/isuhani_1466816208302oWyQc_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501377.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_4/isuhani_1466816208302oWyQc_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501377.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">다 수제 소세지라고 하드라..<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_31/isuhani_1466816208737df6xS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161444769.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 853px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_31/isuhani_1466816208737df6xS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161444769.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_31/isuhani_1466816208737df6xS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161444769.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_294/isuhani_1466816209043pr2iQ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161445039.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"537\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 537px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_294/isuhani_1466816209043pr2iQ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161445039.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_294/isuhani_1466816209043pr2iQ_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161445039.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" />원장님이랑 쌤은 맥주</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">나는 사과쥬스</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅠ<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_185/isuhani_1466816209943lPJbx_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161459191.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 853px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_185/isuhani_1466816209943lPJbx_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161459191.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_185/isuhani_1466816209943lPJbx_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161459191.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_9/isuhani_1466816209584q7IOS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161445301.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"503\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 503px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_9/isuhani_1466816209584q7IOS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161445301.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_9/isuhani_1466816209584q7IOS_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161445301.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">오늘의 마지막 메뉴는 </p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">모듬소세지로..</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">비주얼 참... 먹음직 스럽다&nbsp; ^^</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_132/isuhani_1466816210360064Lv_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161459911.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"648\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 648px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_132/isuhani_1466816210360064Lv_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161459911.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_132/isuhani_1466816210360064Lv_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161459911.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">쌤이 먹기 좋게 잘라주시구<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_183/isuhani_1466816210651SlYlb_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161500328.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_183/isuhani_1466816210651SlYlb_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161500328.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_183/isuhani_1466816210651SlYlb_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161500328.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_291/isuhani_146681621096669Uv7_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161500719.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"550\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 550px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_291/isuhani_146681621096669Uv7_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161500719.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_291/isuhani_146681621096669Uv7_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161500719.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">소세지가 짭짤하니 </p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">맛있는데..</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">어떤거 너무 짜 ㅠ<br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_265/isuhani_1466816211299JAPXY_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501063.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"853\" style=\"cursor: pointer;border-color: rgb(0, 0, 0); rheight: 853px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_265/isuhani_1466816211299JAPXY_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501063.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_265/isuhani_1466816211299JAPXY_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161501063.jpg?type=w3\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">원장님이랑 쌤이랑 이얘기 저얘기 하실때</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">나는 밖에도 한번씩 쳐다보고</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋㅋ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&#8203;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_68/isuhani_1466816211693SUma4_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161458029.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_68/isuhani_1466816211693SUma4_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161458029.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_68/isuhani_1466816211693SUma4_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161458029.jpg?type=w3\"><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><br style=\"clear: both;\" /><img src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_282/isuhani_1466816212099X6P29_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161458668.jpg?type=w80_blur\" width=\"480\" height=\"270\" style=\"cursor: pointer; rheight: 270px; rwidth: 480px;\" id=\"20160625_282/isuhani_1466816212099X6P29_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161458668.jpg\" onclick=\"popview(this, '90000003_000000000000003365758343')\" alt=\"\" class=\"_photoImage\" data-lazy-src=\"https://postfiles.pstatic.net/20160625_282/isuhani_1466816212099X6P29_JPEG/KakaoTalk_20160621_161458668.jpg?type=w3\"></p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">참 즐겁고 재밌던 회식이었다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p><p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">이수한의원 가족들끼리</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">많은 이야기도 하고</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">재밌는 이야기도 하고</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">너무 재밌었다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">너무 웃어서 입이 다 아플정도였어</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">ㅋㅋㅋ</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\">좋은 사람들과 함께 하는 시간은 늘 좋다</p>\r\n<p align=\"center\" style=\"text-align: center;\"><a href=\"http://m.gfmarket.naver.com/sticker/detail/code/line_characters_in_love\" target=\"_blank\"\"><img src=\"https://storep-phinf.pstatic.net/line_characters_in_love/original_4.png?type=p50_50\" alt=\"line_characters_in_love-4\"></a></p></div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t</div>",
